public class RedhatLinuxOperatingSystemImpl
extends LinuxOperatingSystemImpl
implements RedhatLinuxOperatingSystem

An implementation of the model object 'Redhat Linux Operating System'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Boot Loader
  • Desktop
  • Install Date
  • Last Boot Up Time
  • Owner
  • Product Type
  • SE Linux State
